To run this bot, you need to first create a Telegram bot and get the token. you also need to setup ngrok and get the auth token. You can add those tokens to a .env file, and then follow the below steps:

# Install dependencies
python3 -m venv bot-venv
source bot-venv/bin/activate
pip install python-telegram-bot

# Setup  environment variables
cp .env.example .env

# Run the bot
python bot.py
python web_server.py